# Supported Keyboard Shortcuts

* `Ctrl+T` → New tab
* `Ctrl+W` / `Ctrl+F4` → Close tab
* `Ctrl+L` → Focus address bar
* `Ctrl+R` / `F5` → Refresh
* `Esc` → Stop loading
* `Alt+Left` → Back
* `Alt+Right` → Forward
* `Alt+Home` → Open home page
* `Ctrl+Tab` → Next tab
* `Ctrl+Shift+Tab` → Previous tab
* `Ctrl+1` to `Ctrl+8` → Switch to tab number
* `Ctrl+9` → Last tab
* `Ctrl++` → Zoom in
* `Ctrl+-` → Zoom out
* `Ctrl+0` → Reset zoom

